  "detailed_description": "Super Gosu Cars is an arcade style kart racing game for up to 8 local players! Choose your vehicle and driver, put the pedal to the metal, get your drifting skills in gear and make use of powerful items to devastate the competition and claw your way to victory!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Local multiplayer and Steam Remote Play!<br></li><li>1-4 player split screen!<br></li><li>1-8 player top-down view!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/4330dcacdc255eeffcf042a60b7adf79.poster.avif?t=1698407456\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/4330dcacdc255eeffcf042a60b7adf79.webm?t=1698407456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/4330dcacdc255eeffcf042a60b7adf79.mp4?t=1698407456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/6886c7842294a736e794fb3457ab7ab6.avif?t=1698407456\" width=300 height=168 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ITEMS AND POWER-UPS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Homing missiles! Propeller-in-a-box! Giant electro-bombs! Whoa!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/101a9d617f4fa1c4414a75d5d9198845.avif?t=1698407456\" width=280 height=180 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/bee344590c03b02004cf8d2ebf125d65.poster.avif?t=1698407456\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/bee344590c03b02004cf8d2ebf125d65.webm?t=1698407456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/bee344590c03b02004cf8d2ebf125d65.mp4?t=1698407456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MIRROR MODE AND MUTATORS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Spice up your custom tournaments with <strong>Mutators</strong>: Dark Mode, Low Gravity, Big Items..!<br></li><li>Experience all your favourite tracks from the other side with <strong>Mirror Mode</strong>!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/d11e2b1c3c3b08d952daf400cd5e326a.poster.avif?t=1698407456\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/d11e2b1c3c3b08d952daf400cd5e326a.webm?t=1698407456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/d11e2b1c3c3b08d952daf400cd5e326a.mp4?t=1698407456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/9dc9c37592700abe806e459f75b8048c.avif?t=1698407456\" width=280 height=180 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MEET THE SUPER GOSU RACERS AND VEHICLES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Get to know Margaret, Kenta, Penelope, The Professor, Bot-0 and the rest of the gang as they compete in the Super Gosu Cars Grand Prix in vehicles such as the Funkswaggon, Running MXM, Traktor, Classic Estate, Patrol 80 and more!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/f5e14dbc1b459a906c21e0f1d1026eea.avif?t=1698407456\" width=600 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ACHIEVEMENTS AND UNLOCKS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>29 Steam Achievements</strong> and more to come!<br></li><li>Unlock additional drivers, vehicles, tracks, cups, mutators and more as you play!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/e989f23f049e9d11e55b12f69c5a3c67.avif?t=1698407456\" width=600 height=110 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME MODES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Grand Prix</strong>: 8 racers compete in a variety of cups; each with their own set of challenges.<br></li><li><strong>Time Trial</strong>: Hone your driving skills while racing against the clock.<br></li><li><strong>Custom Tournament</strong> Pick and choose your own set of tracks, rules, and more.</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1912560/extras/26e3b5e062e449a5ea68add313c3483e.avif?t=1698407456\" width=600 height=124 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPCOMING FEATURES BEFORE LEAVING EARLY ACCESS</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Ruleset type mutators for Custom Tournament.<br></li><li>Additional drivers and vehicles.<br></li><li>Additional in-game challenges and Steam achievements.<br></li><li>Additional items.<br></li><li>Enhanced audio and sound effects.</li></ul>",
